Adjusted the hero-card width treatment so the route-link list below the diagram occupies the same usable width as the lineage box.

Width-related changes in `website/src/pages/index.module.css`:
- `.sceneDiagram` now declares `width: 100%` and `box-sizing: border-box`
- `.sceneSteps` now declares `width: 100%`
- `.sceneSteps li` now declares `width: 100%`
- `.sceneStepLink` now keeps `width: 100%` with explicit `box-sizing: border-box`

This aligns the four route items with the diagram box above them instead of letting them read as a narrower track.
